data.description: Lots of potential in this spacious home in sought after Maryville location. 5-6 bedrooms, 5 baths. Finished basement with media room, family room, bath, bar area & bedroom. Some storage. Main bedroom/bath and second bedroom on main level with 3 additional bedrooms & 2 baths on upper level, one bedroom on lower level. Needs TLC to make the most of its potential. 3 car garage, fenced yard and walkout lower level. Seller will make no repairs. Being sold as is.
